理<br />\n但返黎果程可以好嚴</blockquote><br />\n1月係NRT返....日本既UO員工超嚴謹...<br />\n<br />\n見幾過人過左限制比人罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n限制係指重量上？</blockquote><br />\nYES"},{"pid":"6789d664869bbb8192d6cfc6649a6bf0d93042f7","tid":111780,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上次淆底咗 將個背囊塞落個hand carry 個gip到  之後諗起都傻 因為根本no one cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n意思係佢會好鬆？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必<br />\n香港飛可能唔理<br />\n但返黎果程可以好嚴</blockquote><br />\n1月係NRT返....日本既UO員工超嚴謹...<br />\n<br />\n見幾過人過左限制比人罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我次次買20kg都用唔晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a263d69799740da23fd98150a69a3a194889e3","tid":111780,"uid":75452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上次淆底咗 將個背囊塞落個hand carry 個gip到  之後諗起都傻 因為根本no one cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n意思係佢會好鬆？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必<br />\n香港飛可能唔理<br />\n但返黎果程可以好嚴</blockquote><br />\n1月係NRT返....日本既UO員工超嚴謹...<br />\n<br />\n見幾過人過左限制比人罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我次次買20kg都用唔晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去程8.3kg 回程11kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a054e6b7498a5df15dba11d1e2db8cff04cd7ab8","tid":111780,"uid":17980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"依家嚴左<br />\n應該太多人超額<br />\n前兩個星期係日本CHECK IN果時會有張紙條寫住checked hand carry扣係個袋度<br />\n不過我諗罰唔罰就都係睇彩數"},{"pid":"fee0c928275df80705fff7503ceafd9dea852b88","tid":111780,"uid":6566,"like